<tree text="Dh&#x101;tukath&#x101;-a&#x1E6D;&#x1E6D;hakath&#x101;" target="text">
  <text>
    <centered> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</centered>
    <gatha type="1">Aṭṭhārasahi  bhedehi, vibhaṅgaṃ mārabhañjano;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Desayitvā mahāvīro, yaṃ tasseva anantaraṃ.</gatha>
    <gatha type="1">Adesayi dhātukathaṃ, dhātubhedappakāsano;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Tassatthaṃ dīpayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</gatha>
  </text>
</tree>
